1318:src/main.cpp  ****             // Keytracking: how much the cutoff base follows pitch. keytrack=1 is
1319:src/main.cpp  ****             // full tracking (cutoff ŌłØ freq); <1 holds the cutoff lower as pitch
1320:src/main.cpp  ****             // rises, for a more consistent tone across the range. (constexpr ŌåÆ
1321:src/main.cpp  ****             // the common keytrack=1 case folds to no powf.)
1322:src/main.cpp  ****             float track_freq = (VOICE.keytrack >= 0.999f)
1323:src/main.cpp  ****                 ? freq
