1353:src/main.cpp  ****         // Three-LED position indicator. Linear "tents" hand off cleanly:
1354:src/main.cpp  ****         //   LED1 (DAC1, middle)       ŌåÆ 1 - 2*|p - 0.5|
1355:src/main.cpp  ****         //   LED2 (DAC2, pos 0 end)    ŌåÆ max(0, 1 - 2*p)
